@base = http://localhost:8088
@videoId = dQw4w9WgXcQ

### Liveness
GET {{base}}/health/live

### State
GET {{base}}/v1/tracks/{{videoId}}

### First miss / cache hit
GET {{base}}/v1/tracks/{{videoId}}/audio

### Range hit
GET {{base}}/v1/tracks/{{videoId}}/audio
Range: bytes=0-99

### Invalid input / SSRF defense
GET {{base}}/v1/tracks/https%3A%2F%2Fexample.com/audio

### Sanitized diagnostic snapshot
GET {{base}}/internal/diagnostics/snapshot
